

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Objective :This is README file for set of Example Programs of OpenCL-Pthreads.

Written :May 2012
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------



Following codes are present in the directory :


1. openclPthreadMultiGPUVectorAddition-v1.0.c
2. openclPthreadMultiGPUMatrixVectMult-v1.0.c





Compilation and Execution :

1. Go in the correponding directory.
2. Type 'make -f Makefile-Opencl_Pthreads'
3. To run, give
        < executable > <arguments>

